name: mvLA_mix
description:
All example images were processed with highres.fix.

I made this model to add some lines on top of MeinaMix.

Settings

Recommend: Clip skip 2 Sampler: Euler a Steps:30-40

CFG scale:6-10 Vae: The model already includes VAE, so you don't need to use VAE.

Highres.fix:RealESRGAN_x4plus_anime_6B

Hires steps:10 Denoising strength:0.3 Upscale by: 1.5+

merge model list: meinamix_meinaV7, vividicimix, and some Lora models with added lines.
